<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-1678] Convert to image problem</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-1678</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I build maven repo for pdfbox 2.0 version from git.&lt;br/&gt;
I need convert pdf to image.&lt;br/&gt;
In pdf used font Arial from windows but i get not readable image.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
